{"tid":1189450,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] LEFT 4 DEAD 2 多人Coop","createTime":"2019-06-06T20:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:44.000Z","uid":1402,"like":9,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3a0563eba0f4167832db0d6d27171789433c85","tid":1189450,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T20:22:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>LEFT 4 DEAD</del></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LEFT 24 DEAD</span></span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，半年前我開過24人L4D2 Coop Server一排<br />\n如果你有印象嘅話，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過應該冇人玩過小薯ser</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後因為一籃子因素同Final Year關係，我都冇咩時間打機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住就冇再開落去，直到依家先有時間重新開番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逢<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五六日10點</span></ins>(大約時間)先開波</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於當日玩咩圖就會係discord放download link <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要都係非官圖，甚至會翻炒之前玩過嘅map <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於in-game mic太廢，我地唔諗住用黎溝通用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期五六日10點 即係今晚10點(7/6/19)會開呀 <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskysmile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskysmile.gif&h=1f294c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單講下個server setting同埋規則<br />\n講明係多人ser<br />\n難度當然係set<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">專家</span></del>困難<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多人玩，當然唔少得TK啦<br />\n玩落同玩四人專家冇咩分別，真正嘅敵人係隊友呀 <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskyhaha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskyhaha.gif&h=5c6cafb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">遇到TK，唔好嬲</span><br />\n我都食唔少，亦唔小心TK到自己友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多屍潮多特感呢D更加係例牌野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇呢D就唔好玩啦 十幾個打幾隻屍 R痕咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁嘅情況下，個ser係非常講求合作性先過到關(我都計唔到一場會死幾多個，救幾多個) <code>睇Gameplay1</code>，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔比自己一個狗衝去安全室</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使你單拖衝到安全室都唔代表入到去架<br />\nadmin is watching you 後果自負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n命仔緊要，所以有裝到買野系統<br />\n比大家買槍、自救之類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然要殺下屍、特感賺下分先買到野<br />\n其實我係唔想太hardcore，變到太難玩<br />\n大家一齊輕輕鬆鬆過關咁樣幾好呀<br />\n<br />\n唔多唔少嘅map都有伏位，唔好自己行咗去，大家一齊行<br />\n有伏緊係要齊齊中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，我估大家玩得多會悶<br />\n所以我之後會隨機比幾位玩家做特感玩下<br />\n改變下個玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩家對玩家，咁樣個難度又會唔同咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個計劃會做一系列嘅測試先會正式落實</span><br />\ne.g. :比幾多個玩家做特感，特感玩家血量方面又點樣處理<br />\n呢D都係要諗好同試好先得，我唔想有一面倒嘅情況出現<br />\n整得唔好 咁樣大家都玩得唔開心 無謂啦</del> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins>其實半年前已經測試緊，跟住落黎我會繼續做fine tuning<br />\n確保各位玩得開心同維持番個遊戲平衡</ins> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGameplay: <br />\n1.論燃燒彈與合作性: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/29566686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F29566686&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=5960dfb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/29566686</a><br />\n2. 論唔好幫自己立Flag嘅重要性: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/36766286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F36766286&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=fcc1da76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/36766286</a><br />\n3. 過<del>馬路</del>月台要小心(?): <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/22393152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F22393152&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=4f163ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/22393152</a><br />\n4. 論手殘admin處事方法: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/32206368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F32206368&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=045f4c50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/32206368</a><br />\n5. on9真係冇極限架: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/videos/19414636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fvideos%2F19414636&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a3155bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/videos/19414636</a><br />\n6. 安全室又真係好安全下: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0vYEbDazBrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0vYEbDazBrU&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=a093e53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0vYEbDazBrU</a><br />\n7. (特感玩家Gameplay) 唔該等埋: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKpcbC_Xj1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOKpcbC_Xj1g&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=88353f6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKpcbC_Xj1g</a><br />\n<br />\n好隊友都離你而去系列<br />\n1. AFK嘅下場?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UF3W2Kc7DRI?t=37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUF3W2Kc7DRI%3Ft%3D37&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=81efccf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UF3W2Kc7DRI?t=37</a><br />\n2. 上唔到船嘅下場?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkHaxxE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkHaxxE.png&h=23969b94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有mic，記得開咪呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有事叫admin幫手就得架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係事必要你入嘅，但你要入咗黎先入到ser玩咁解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://husky.moe/l24ddiscord\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhusky.moe%2Fl24ddiscord&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=86f313fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://husky.moe/l24ddiscord</a><br />\nTelegram Group: <a href=\"https://husky.moe/l24dtelegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhusky.moe%2Fl24dtelegram&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=8b891dd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://husky.moe/l24dtelegram</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我都知大家會tldr</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efc627a425a3d056904568947751a5bc36e923b","tid":1189450,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a47b803d4a6e9c12c3a3540b4754c1c6d6ea3a","tid":1189450,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23d25b02c438f69eef9f1f4fb4b55a48d3fa8bd","tid":1189450,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"